surprising or shocking because of not having been previously known about.

86
00:05:33,599 --> 00:05:37,039
Scientists are hoping that the mucus' absorptive qualities,

87
00:05:37,599 --> 00:05:41,680
its ability to absorb liquids and other substances and hold them,

88
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:45,359
will allow it to track particles of plastic floating in the sea,

89
00:05:45,359 --> 00:05:48,399
making jellyfish mucus a magnet for pollution,

90
